    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This power unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver 333 hp with a surgical 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS bulletproofing. The suspension geometry remains precise, benefiting from refreshed bushings and a recent four-wheel alignment. Finished in Carbon Black with a driver-centric interior, this M3 offers a pure mechanical connection and remains a benchmark for chassis balance and linear power delivery.",
